Description: Deepin Water - Desktop drinking water reminder
 A fun and non-intrusive desktop water drinking reminder application.
 Features animated characters (skeleton dance, lion jump, funny guy)
 to remind you to drink water regularly.
 .
 Supports customizable reminder intervals, animation themes,
 system tray integration, and drinking history tracking.
